text: Live at Kafé Hærverk is a live album by Swedish band Brainbombs. It was recorded at Kafé Hærverk on the 27th of May, 2022 and released on the 6th of October, 2023. Brainbombs has performed at Kafé Hærverk a total of 4 times. == Track listing == == References == Category:Live albums Category:2023 albums Category:Brainbombs albums Category:Rock albums
title: Live at Kafé Hærverk (Brainbombs album)
